Packages 
Package Description
application
main application for the game
configurations
Configurations package to store all the configurations of the game
controllers
controllers based on input
demos
example projects to show how to use this framework
demos.controllerdemos
a group of demos showing the use of controllers
demos.controllerdemos.arrowcontrollerexample
An example of the use of the ArrowKeyController
demos.controllerdemos.mousecontrollerexample
mouse controller demo with mouse and keyboard controls
demos.helloworld
Just a simple hello world being displayed
demos.physicsdemo
demo that shows the physics capabilities of this framework
demos.spritedemo
demo displaying the sprites
demos.statesaving
same as demo at demos.controllerdemos.mousecontrollerexample except the state is stored locally on exit
framework
The main framework package
graphics
a package for graphics control
input
input types and controllers
projects
package made to include any full projects made from this framework
projects.virtualworld
A virtual world that saves the state of the game on exit locally
testing
Testing package
uiitems
A package for all the items on the screen
uiitems.entities
entities containing properties such as health and moving options
uiitems.gravityitems
items affected by gravity
uiitems.interactiveitems
items that can interact with or be interacted with other items
util
Utilities that can be accessed publicly for this project
webapplet
uses the japplet class to create a web applet from the javafx code
